  "texts": [
    "The metadata annotations enable us to further analyze the determinants of model performance.",
    "We find large discrepancies across political biases and misinformation forms, but have also shown that increased diversity has a positive effect on generalization.",
    "While publisher-level labelling introduces noise, we believe the increased scale, diversity, and affluence of metadata make up for this.",
    "The first two properties can enable OoD generalization or robustness, whereas the latter enables evaluation, analysis and potentially generalization-aware training.",
    "We make the dataset publicly available, and hope it will serve as a resource for OoD generalization-focused training and evaluation."
